criteria.textblock:
Inclusion criteria:

  -  Subjects with colorectal adenomatous polyps greater than 1 cm in maximum diameter not
     suitable to immediate complete removal;

  -  Normal renal and hepatic function;

  -  WHO Performance status=0;

Exclusion Criteria:

  -  Presence of hyperplastic polyps and/or flat adenomas;

  -  Subjects with pre-existing colorectal cancer;

  -  Presence of carcinomatous tissue in adenoma;
